     500         - NTST  (Step of printing data for T/P contours)
       1         - LCOND (e- therm conduction is off/0, on/1)
       4         - KON   (Type of thermal conductivity approximation 1,2,3)
       0         - KONF  (0-film, 1-bulk target)
  40000.000000   - WIDTH (Width of the laser pulse on a half maximum [nm])
      1.000000   - DURAT (Laser pulse duration [psec])  
      0.000d-11  - ENRIN (energy J) 0.8J/cm^2  2.659d-11